==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: fascinated
<hw>fascinated</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>having the
attention fixed by a sense of wonder.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> hypnotized, hypnotised, mesmerized, mesmerised,
spellbound, transfixed.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>intensely interested in or attracted by; <as>as, I'm
very interested in birds; in fact I'm <ex>fascinated</ex> by
them</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>fascinating</ent>⟦br⟧
